English: You've put bounty in previous season. Cannot put bounty tow seasons in a row
Cumulative play score of all users

At the end of the season, you will be rewarded based on your contribution rate.
As your contribution rate increases compared to the accumulated play scores of all users, the type and amount of rewards increase.
The amount of reward increases multiplied depending on the number of participants.
15% of the total bounty amount in operation is paid to all users according to their contribution rate.
5% of the total bounty in operation is randomly paid to one person.
You can earn rewards when you reach each floor. (Seasonal Reset)
At the end of the season, you will be rewarded based on the amount of bounty you paid.
5% of the total bounty in operation is randomly paid to one person.
